    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.日本經營者、員工、顧客的關係。<br>2.日商職場三法。<br>3.日本的禮儀、規範。<br>4.心理學概述。<br>",
        "en": "1.The relationships among the employers, employee and the customers in Japan.<br>2.The 3 policies and tolls of the Japanese Industry.<br>3.The manner and rules in Japan.<br>4.Introduction to Psychology."
